Rallos Zek worshippers start out dubious to Coldain.<br>
<br>
All race/class/religion combos EXCEPT Rallos Zek worshippers start out KOS to velious giants.<br>
Rallos Zek worshippers start out dubious to at least some of the giants (not sure if all, tho).<br>
<br>
